<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your Challenge Match score is in...</h1>
    <p>
      The challenged player, <%= "#{@match.challenged_player.first_name} #{@match.challenged_player.last_name}" %>, has submitted the score for your challenge match played on <%= @match.played_at.to_date.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %>.
    </p>
    <% if @match.challenged_player.id == @match.winner %>
      <p>The challenged player won the match with the following scores:</p>
      <p>
        <%= @match.challenged_player_game1 %> : <%= @match.challenger_game1 %>,
        <%= @match.challenged_player_game2 %> : <%= @match.challenger_game2 %>
        <% unless @match.challenger_game3.to_i == 0 and @match.challenged_player_game3.to_i == 0 %>
          , <%= @match.challenged_player_game3 %> : <%= @match.challenger_game3 %>
        <% end %>
      </p>
      <p>Your rank remains unchanged.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>You won the match with the following scores:</p>
      <p>
        <%= @match.challenger_game1 %> : <%= @match.challenged_player_game1 %>,
        <%= @match.challenger_game2 %> : <%= @match.challenged_player_game2 %>
        <% unless @match.challenger_game3.to_i == 0 and @match.challenged_player_game3.to_i == 0 %>
          , <%= @match.challenger_game3 %> : <%= @match.challenged_player_game3 %>
        <% end %>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Your new rank is <%= @match.challenged_player.rank %></strong></p>
    <% end %>
    <br><br>
    <p>Thanks for participating!</p>
  </body>
</html>